Interface AceFileDataStore

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, ContigDataStore<AceAssembledRead,AceContig>, DataStore<AceContig>

    public interface AceFileDataStore
extends ContigDataStore<AceAssembledRead,AceContig>
    AceFileDataStore is a ContigDataStore for AceContigs that are contained in a single .ace file.

    • Method Detail

      • getNumberOfTotalReads

        long getNumberOfTotalReads()
                    throws DataStoreException
        Get the total number of reads over all the contigs in the datastore. This number may be different than the total number stated in the header of the ace file for two reasons:
        1. Some contigs may be filtered out of this datastore depending on the parameters used when constructing this AceFileDataStore instance.
        2. Some reads in a contig may be excluded because they are either invalid or don't provide any coverage
        Returns:
        the total number of reads in all the contigs in this datastore, will always be ≥ 0.
        Throws:
        DataStoreException - if there is a problem reading the data from this datastore.
